keys

@NonNull abstract fun keys(): MutableList<K>

Returns a list of keys of all entries in the cache or a non-null empty list. The order of the entries in the list is implementation dependent.

Return
MutableList<K>: A list of keys of all entries in the cache or a non-null empty list (use List#isEmpty() to check).
